WEBVTT

00:00:01.362 --> 00:00:07.030
DVADTSAT' PYATAYA FEVRALYA TYSYACHA DEVYAT'SOT DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO GOD. GODA.

00:00:07.030 --> 00:00:09.675
MERI Gotler. Gotler.

00:00:09.765 --> 00:00:13.830
INTER- INTERV'YUIRUYUSHCHIY: Khaim Bargman.

00:00:13.830 --> 00:00:18.050
GOROD: KAUNAS. STRANA: LITVA. YAZYK: Yidish.

00:00:18.410 --> 00:00:21.060
POCHEMY DEVYANOSTO SHESTOGO?

00:00:24.379 --> 00:00:27.832
haynt iz der, finf un tsvantsikter FEVRAL',

00:00:27.872 --> 00:00:30.532
toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsiktn yor.

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:32.912
mir zaynen in Lite,

00:00:33.812 --> 00:00:35.088
in Kovne,

00:00:35.483 --> 00:00:40.000
un mir heybn on in- dem intervyu mit MERI Gotler.

00:00:50.090 --> 00:00:52.860
 f-...

00:00:56.442 --> 00:00:58.022
far di milkhome...

00:01:00.240 --> 00:01:06.160
⟨er vet gebn a simen⟩. er vet gebn a simen. "ikh bin geborn gevorn..." sh!

00:01:06.183 --> 00:01:07.340
er vet gebn a simen.

00:01:06.752 --> 00:01:07.893
ikh bin...

00:01:07.340 --> 00:01:09.610
sh! er vet gebn a simen.

00:01:09.926 --> 00:01:11.810
UNK

00:01:12.912 --> 00:01:14.419
ikh bin geborn

00:01:14.419 --> 00:01:16.078
fun draysiktn yor.

00:01:18.250 --> 00:01:21.714
 ikh hob gehat nokh finf shvester.

00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:25.730
 kh'hob gehat a tatn, a mamen.

00:01:28.605 --> 00:01:33.290
mir hobn ale gelebt. s'iz geven freylekh. s'iz geven undz gut.

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:38.270
nakher hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:01:38.477 --> 00:01:44.428
 antshuldikt a bisele. dertseylt, undz a bisl merer ven, v- vegn ayer mishpokhe lebn far der milkhome,

00:01:45.210 --> 00:01:48.020
vegn ayere tate-mame...

00:01:48.130 --> 00:01:50.301
nu, di mame...

00:01:50.205 --> 00:01:51.930
vi hot geheysn ayer muter?

00:01:51.353 --> 00:01:54.290
Ite. Ite Gotler.

00:01:54.829 --> 00:02:00.330
 der tate hot geheysn Shmulye Gotler.

00:02:01.174 --> 00:02:04.172
mit vos hot zikh b- basheftikt ayer foter?

00:02:03.670 --> 00:02:06.213
mayn foter iz geven a shuster.

00:02:06.304 --> 00:02:08.450
er flegt makhn naye shikh.

00:02:10.836 --> 00:02:11.910
un...

00:02:10.860 --> 00:02:13.498
nu, dernokh iz der foter krank gevorn.

00:02:13.498 --> 00:02:15.596
er hot arbetn nit gekent.

00:02:15.602 --> 00:02:17.852
hot di mame ongehoybn neyen,

00:02:17.852 --> 00:02:20.979
flegt zi neyen dortn tshekholn, shikhlekh,

00:02:21.154 --> 00:02:23.595
un zi flegt fardinen far di kinder.

00:02:24.765 --> 00:02:28.623
di kinder zaynen gevorn gresere. iz avek eyne arbetn.

00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:31.984
di tsveyte iz avek arbetn, di eltere.

00:02:31.984 --> 00:02:35.368
zey hobn zikh fardint shoyn far zikh, oyf ontsuton,

00:02:35.368 --> 00:02:37.888
un di mame hot undz alemen gekormet.

00:02:37.675 --> 00:02:42.550
un vos hobn, vos hobn geton ayere shvester? un zogt, bite zeyere nemen.

00:02:41.180 --> 00:02:43.740
mayn shvester hot gearbet in,

00:02:43.740 --> 00:02:47.018
eyne hot zikh, eyne hot gearbet in a shnayderay.

00:02:46.606 --> 00:02:48.390
vos, vi iz ir nomen ge-...?

00:02:47.513 --> 00:02:52.547
dos iz geven di eltste, Sheyne-Taybe. zi gefint zikh itster in Argentine.

00:02:52.547 --> 00:02:55.353
zi iz avekgeforn in akht un draysiktn yor.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.854
ir hot opgenumen a tante.

00:02:57.854 --> 00:03:01.125
dos iz geven di mame's, dem foter's a shvester.

00:03:02.599 --> 00:03:05.456
nu, un, di tsveyte hot,

00:03:05.456 --> 00:03:09.917
gem- flegt makhn shleykes. zi hot gearbet bay a balebos.

00:03:09.834 --> 00:03:12.580
 un vi iz ir nom- vi iz der nomen geven fun di ts-...?

00:03:10.260 --> 00:03:13.578
z- zi flegt shleyke-... Zelde Gotler.

00:03:14.513 --> 00:03:19.630
di drite, Khaye Gotler, iz oykh avek arbetn.

00:03:19.630 --> 00:03:23.570
zi flegt zikh lernen shtrikn bay a shtrikeray.

00:03:25.245 --> 00:03:31.736
un mir zaynen geven dray shvesterlekh, di kleyne: Raytsele, Basele, un ikh.

00:03:32.012 --> 00:03:34.440
un di eltere ayere shvester,

00:03:34.133 --> 00:03:34.950
UNK

00:03:34.440 --> 00:03:37.811
 zey f-, hobn gearbet bay di yidishe balebatim?

00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:41.720
 ale hobn gearbet bay yidishe balebatim, ale.

00:03:41.631 --> 00:03:44.410
un vos far a shprakh hot ir geredt in der shtub?

00:03:43.710 --> 00:03:45.236
 yidish.

00:03:45.495 --> 00:03:47.744
mir hobn ale geredt nor yidish.

00:03:47.744 --> 00:03:51.783
mir hobn gekent litvish oykh, ober in shtub flegn mir reydn yidish.

00:03:51.823 --> 00:03:55.290
un ayere shvester hobn, bakumen epes bildung?

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:56.680
 keyn zakh nit,

00:03:56.680 --> 00:04:01.065
vayl zey flegn endikn tsu fir, tsu finf klasn un ⟨zikh⟩ geyn lernen a fakh,

00:04:01.398 --> 00:04:02.398
ayer...

00:04:01.425 --> 00:04:03.731
vayle s'iz geven zeyer shver der lebn.

00:04:03.501 --> 00:04:06.380
 tsu s'iz geven ayer mishpokhe a farmeglekhe tsu a o-...?

00:04:06.015 --> 00:04:12.247
nu, arbeter mentshn., nu, oybe di mame hot gearbet aleyn, kent ir zikh forshteln

00:04:12.247 --> 00:04:13.957
vi s'iz geven farmeglekh.

00:04:14.166 --> 00:04:20.859
 s'iz geven a bruder in Amerike, mayn foter's bruder, in Amerike. flegt er undz shikn peklekh.

00:04:20.764 --> 00:04:23.070
vi hot geheysn ayer foter's bruder in Amerike?

00:04:22.603 --> 00:04:23.980
Gotlib,

00:04:24.004 --> 00:04:25.040
⟨ay- e-⟩...

00:04:24.055 --> 00:04:25.264
Khaim.

00:04:25.040 --> 00:04:26.175
Khaim Gotlib?

00:04:25.675 --> 00:04:27.221
Khaim Gotlib.

00:04:27.868 --> 00:04:30.005
un vos hot geton ayer muter aleyn?

00:04:30.045 --> 00:04:33.960
nu, a shnayderke, ober zi flegt, beys der,

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:36.569
foter hot gearbet, hot zi, hot zi nit geneyt.

00:04:36.593 --> 00:04:40.468
zi flegt darfn in shtub, a KHO- a baleboste in shtub iz zi geven.

00:04:40.660 --> 00:04:47.994
un nakher, az der foter iz krank gevorn, hot zi shoyn gemuzt onheybn neyen, un zi flegt helfn kormenen undz, di kinder.

00:04:47.764 --> 00:04:50.458
un vos iz geven di krankeyt fun ayer foter?

00:04:51.038 --> 00:04:53.479
im hot ongehoybn treyslen a hant.

00:04:54.582 --> 00:04:56.736
un er hot zikh gevendet tsu doktoyrim?

00:04:56.758 --> 00:05:00.360
 nu, UNK er iz keyn mol nit gegangen bay keyn doktoyrim.

00:05:00.370 --> 00:05:05.320
⟨er fleg⟩, er iz nit gegangen; s'hot ongehoybn treyslen di hant, arbetn hot er nit gekent, un,...

00:05:05.854 --> 00:05:07.096
un nakher,

00:05:07.947 --> 00:05:11.552
in, e- in f- eyn un fertsiktn yor,

00:05:12.553 --> 00:05:14.656
ven s'hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome...

00:05:16.170 --> 00:05:19.753
 ikh bin far di milkhome geven oyf kanikl

00:05:19.877 --> 00:05:21.271
in Yaneve,

00:05:21.936 --> 00:05:24.039
beys di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn.

00:05:24.366 --> 00:05:29.020
un, di ta- di tante, mayn mame's shvester,

00:05:29.020 --> 00:05:32.310
Yudes hot men ir gerufn, Yudes Shmit.

00:05:32.517 --> 00:05:34.856
zi hot oykh gehat fir kinder.

00:05:35.115 --> 00:05:39.693
di nemen gedenk ikh shoyn nit alemen's. kh'veys nor Rase,

00:05:39.693 --> 00:05:40.999
un,...

00:05:43.688 --> 00:05:45.960
 vi hot men gerufn dem...?

00:05:46.692 --> 00:05:48.694
M- Moyshe, dakht mir.

00:05:49.273 --> 00:05:54.464
nu, ikh hob shoyn VOOBSHCHE fargesn. s'iz ariber fuftsik yor; ikh ken nit gedenken alts.

00:05:55.011 --> 00:05:59.578
dortn, az ikh bin geven, hot di m- mume gezogt,

00:06:00.343 --> 00:06:03.459
"Merele, gey nit, blayb mit undz!

00:06:04.140 --> 00:06:07.829
vos iz dir vikhtik, tsu du bist bay di mamen, tsu bay undz?"

00:06:08.038 --> 00:06:10.802
zog ikh, "neyn, ikh vil bay di mamen."

00:06:10.802 --> 00:06:15.423
hot der onkl genumen mir, mitn letstn AVTOBUS avekgefirt,

00:06:16.341 --> 00:06:19.569
un ikh bin gekumen tsu forn in Kovne. er hot mir a-

00:06:19.569 --> 00:06:21.948
arayngezetst in letstn AVTOBUS,

00:06:21.948 --> 00:06:24.570
un avekgef- un ikh bin gekumen in Kovne.

00:06:24.576 --> 00:06:27.439
ikh kum tsu geyn in Kovne, shteyt mayn

00:06:27.613 --> 00:06:31.380
tate avekgeshtelt un ⟨k- S-⟩ kukt oyfn himl.

00:06:31.613 --> 00:06:36.082
er hot mir nit gezen glaykh; ikh hob im derzen. zog ikh, "tate, vos shteystu do?"

00:06:36.082 --> 00:06:40.027
zogt er, "Merele, mir klaybn zikh tsu loyfn oyf Yaneve."

00:06:41.248 --> 00:06:44.029
zog ikh, "tsurik oyf Yaneve?" zogt er, "ye."

00:06:44.029 --> 00:06:48.030
un mir zaynen ale, zey hobn genumen dortn peklekh mit zikh,

00:06:48.030 --> 00:06:51.081
un mir zaynen tsu fus avek oyf Yaneve.

00:06:51.542 --> 00:06:54.000
dos iz geven der ershter tog fun der milkhome?

00:06:53.398 --> 00:06:56.320
der ershter tog fun UNK, ye.

00:06:56.436 --> 00:06:58.455
der ershter tog fun milkhome.

00:06:58.073 --> 00:07:01.425
antshuldikt a bisl. ikh vil aykh fregn a bisl far der milkhome.

00:07:01.482 --> 00:07:04.660
vu hot ir zikh aleyn gelernt, far der milkhome?

00:07:03.861 --> 00:07:07.550
ikh hob zikh gelernt in a yidishe shul, bay Raynesikhen.

00:07:08.215 --> 00:07:09.643
dos iz in Kovne?

00:07:09.396 --> 00:07:10.773
in Kovne.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.461
efsher gedenkt ir oyf vosere gas?

00:07:11.792 --> 00:07:13.625
 DAUKŠOS,

00:07:13.834 --> 00:07:15.230
in altshtot,

00:07:15.190 --> 00:07:17.290
un vos hot ir zikh gelernt in di yidishe shul?

00:07:15.230 --> 00:07:16.511
oyf DAUKŠO-...

00:07:17.682 --> 00:07:20.302
m'hot undz gelernt yidish, litvish,

00:07:20.302 --> 00:07:23.660
zingen, tantsn. alts hot men gelernt.

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:30.011
 di lererke undzere iz geven Raynes,

00:07:30.439 --> 00:07:31.783
Raynesikhe,

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:35.698
un di lererke hot aykh gelernt alts, say litvish, say yidish?

00:07:31.992 --> 00:07:33.336
di familye.

00:07:35.012 --> 00:07:40.155
s'iz geven nokh a lererke; s'iz geven Puner, a lere- a lererke undzere,

00:07:40.155 --> 00:07:44.840
un nakher iz geven nokh a lerer vos hot undz gelernt zingen, ober di familye ge-

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:46.346
gedenk ikh shoyn nit.

00:07:45.846 --> 00:07:48.034
un matematike hot men aykh gelernt?

00:07:47.213 --> 00:07:51.189
nu, vi den? gelernt rekhenen, alts.

00:07:50.560 --> 00:07:52.340
un v- ver hot gelernt rekhenen?

00:07:52.917 --> 00:07:56.404
di zelbike lererke vos, Raynesikhe.

00:07:57.152 --> 00:07:59.880
un, hebreish hot men aykh oykh gelernt?

00:07:57.388 --> 00:07:58.344
nu...

00:07:58.790 --> 00:08:00.068
 neyn.

00:08:00.068 --> 00:08:02.670
ikh hob nit gelernt in keyn hebreishe shul.

00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:04.554
mir hobn gelernt nor yidish.

00:08:04.037 --> 00:08:06.710
un keyn hebreishe shprakh iz in algemeyn bay aykh nisht geven?

00:08:05.910 --> 00:08:08.469
nit geven in undzer klas.

00:08:09.150 --> 00:08:11.456
in undzer shul iz dos nit geven.

00:08:10.551 --> 00:08:14.122
vifl yor hot ir zikh bavizn tsu lernen far der milkhome?

00:08:14.922 --> 00:08:19.236
 dray klasn hob ikh geendikt far di milkhome.

00:08:19.697 --> 00:08:22.546
un ir v- ir UNK un vos hot zikh gebitn

00:08:22.546 --> 00:08:25.659
ven s'zaynen arayn in fertsiktn yor di rusn in Lite?

00:08:25.659 --> 00:08:28.618
epes vos hot zikh gebitn in ayer ler- in ayer lebn?

00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:31.537
men hot undz aribergefirt in a ander shul,

00:08:31.914 --> 00:08:34.003
beys di rusn zaynen arayn.

00:08:34.003 --> 00:08:38.184
nu, un, men hot undz gegebn a besere dire,

00:08:38.260 --> 00:08:40.363
beys di rusn zaynen arayn.

00:08:41.347 --> 00:08:43.150
s'iz gevorn beser

00:08:43.150 --> 00:08:46.601
in eyn, in, in fertsiktn yor ven di rusn zaynen arayn.

00:08:46.601 --> 00:08:48.867
men hot undz oysgebesert dem lebn.

00:08:49.465 --> 00:08:52.395
nu, ober dos iz geven nit lang.

00:08:53.025 --> 00:08:55.331
es hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:08:56.468 --> 00:08:59.750
hot men glaykh dem foter geshosn

00:08:59.978 --> 00:09:01.830
oyfn zibetn fort.

00:09:02.121 --> 00:09:05.760
un vi hot, v-, vi hot men im farkhapt, dem foter? gedenkt ir?

00:09:04.180 --> 00:09:08.561
 mir zaynen in Yaneve geven, hot men undz dokh alemen

00:09:08.905 --> 00:09:10.952
farkhapt dortn,

00:09:10.952 --> 00:09:14.096
un men hot undz umgekert tsurik in Kovne.

00:09:15.857 --> 00:09:18.450
s'zaynen gegangen mit di vayse,

00:09:19.553 --> 00:09:20.860
orem-bandn?

00:09:20.571 --> 00:09:23.599
m- mit di vayse bender oyf di hent,

00:09:23.599 --> 00:09:26.465
un zey hobn undz gefirt tsurik oyf Kovne.

00:09:26.083 --> 00:09:28.490
ver zaynen geven di, mit di vayse bender?

00:09:28.108 --> 00:09:30.570
nu, s'iz geven, Litviner.

00:09:31.568 --> 00:09:33.418
nu, un,

00:09:33.475 --> 00:09:35.443
nakher hot men undz gehaltn

00:09:36.107 --> 00:09:38.075
in Slabodke,

00:09:38.217 --> 00:09:41.470
lebn INKARAS, s'iz dortn geven a groyse grub.

00:09:41.470 --> 00:09:43.840
hot men undz gehaltn epes durkh nakht,

00:09:43.853 --> 00:09:47.239
un nakher hot men undz avekgefirt oyfn zibetn fort.

00:09:46.873 --> 00:09:48.700
mitn tatn nokh tsuzamen?

00:09:47.768 --> 00:09:50.006
mitn tatn tsuzamen.

00:09:50.063 --> 00:09:58.680
m'hot undz avekgefirt oyfn zibetn fort, zaynen mir dortn geven tsvey vokhn mistome. ikh ken nit gedenken; ikh bin nokh geven a kind.

00:10:00.643 --> 00:10:02.180
un nakher

00:10:02.180 --> 00:10:08.872
iz mayn shvesterl, di mame hot gegebn epes a shtikl broyt mit varenye durkhtsugebn farn tatn.

00:10:09.452 --> 00:10:14.626
iz hot er shoyn nit gekent geyn; er iz shoyn oyf ale fir gekro- tsugekrokhn tsu ir.

00:10:15.612 --> 00:10:17.448
un zi hot dos opgegebn.

00:10:17.448 --> 00:10:19.706
un nakher hot men mir,

00:10:19.729 --> 00:10:26.000
nokh a shvesterl, Raytselen un Baselen, di dray, undz dray, di klenere shvesterlekh,

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:27.840
zaynen mir geven mit di mamen,

00:10:28.167 --> 00:10:30.894
vayl di eltste, Zelde,

00:10:30.900 --> 00:10:33.239
iz geven shoyn khasene gehat.

00:10:33.263 --> 00:10:35.535
zi hot gelebt in Slabodke.

00:10:35.895 --> 00:10:38.575
ikh vel, vayter dertseyln fun ir,

00:10:35.993 --> 00:10:36.993
u-...

00:10:38.575 --> 00:10:41.390
nor itster vel ikh endikn mitn zibetn fort.

00:10:41.565 --> 00:10:43.010
beys ikh bin,

00:10:43.050 --> 00:10:46.625
di shvesterl hot zikh shoyn umgekert, ⟨hot zi⟩ gezogt, "mame," zogt zi, "der

00:10:46.625 --> 00:10:48.495
tate ken shoyn nit geyn."

00:10:48.771 --> 00:10:56.358
nu, ober mir hobn helfn keyn zakh nit gekent, vayl m'hot VOOBSHCHE nit tsugelozn. dos iz geven eyn mol vos m'hot im tsugelozn gebn a shtikl broyt.

00:10:57.620 --> 00:11:04.521
 un beys mir zaynen geven oyfn zibetn fort, hot men gekhapt meydlekh yunge,

00:11:04.521 --> 00:11:10.300
un men hot zey oykh, flegt men khapn fun di gasn, di meydlekh, un brengen oyfn zibetn fort.

00:11:10.300 --> 00:11:14.229
di meydlekh flegt men IZNASILOVen, un me flegt zey avekshisn.

00:11:14.370 --> 00:11:16.861
dos hobn shoyn geton di daytshn dortn.

00:11:17.155 --> 00:11:20.340
ir hot, gezen dos mit ayere oygn, vi m'hot gvaldik-...?

00:11:18.808 --> 00:11:26.264
mit mayne oygn hobn mir dos nit gekent zen. mir zaynen geven ineveynik in fort un men hot undz afile nit aroysgelozn oyfn gas.

00:11:26.264 --> 00:11:28.137
mir zaynen geven ale farmakhte.

00:11:28.137 --> 00:11:31.478
un do hot men eyn meydl arayngelozn in fort,

00:11:31.478 --> 00:11:33.433
m'hot ir opgelozn,

00:11:33.574 --> 00:11:36.684
hot zi dertseylt di mamen, zogt zi, "ir veyst, Ite,

00:11:36.684 --> 00:11:39.896
s'iz geven a groyser pogrom in Slabodke,

00:11:40.577 --> 00:11:45.442
oyf ⟨Kriktshukaytshu⟩, un dortn," zogt zi, hot men avekgeharget di gantse

00:11:45.442 --> 00:11:47.788
familye fun mayn shvester:

00:11:47.788 --> 00:11:52.010
dem man, a shvoger, dem shver,

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:54.170
di shviger,

00:11:54.170 --> 00:11:59.707
un ale fraynt; zey zaynen zikh tsunoyfgekumen. beys di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn, zaynen zey tsunoyfgekumen zikh in di shtub.

00:11:59.916 --> 00:12:02.629
hot men draytsn mentshn oysgeshosn.

00:12:02.629 --> 00:12:05.093
mayn shvester iz geblibn geranet,

00:12:05.093 --> 00:12:08.274
un der shver iz geblibn in gantsn nit geshosn,

00:12:08.274 --> 00:12:13.290
vayl di pulyes iz arayn in mayn shvoger, in ir man, in mayn shvester's.

00:12:13.332 --> 00:12:15.860
aha. vos zaynen pulyes? koyln, ya?

00:12:14.732 --> 00:12:16.852
vos m'hot gesh- ya,

00:12:16.977 --> 00:12:18.084
di koyln.

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:22.944
un dan, ven di banditn zaynen shoyn aroysgegangen,

00:12:23.203 --> 00:12:29.039
hot zikh mayn shvester UNK hot zikh ongehoybn bavegn, un zi zet az der shver iz arayn

00:12:29.039 --> 00:12:32.378
bay zikh in tsimer, vu s'iz geven zayne ale...

00:12:33.666 --> 00:12:38.790
di... nu, vos men davnt, di, di...

00:12:37.665 --> 00:12:39.616
di makhshirim fun davnen.

00:12:39.437 --> 00:12:40.548
fun davnen.

00:12:40.548 --> 00:12:46.738
un er iz arayn un er zogt, "gotenyu, gotenyu, mistome az m'hot geshosn, hot men zey gedarft shisn."

00:12:47.250 --> 00:12:50.281
un di shvester hot derhert vi er redt, vi er...

00:12:50.338 --> 00:12:52.419
zogt zi, "shver,

00:12:52.419 --> 00:12:56.300
zet, es lebt dokh nokh di, di, di shviger.

00:12:56.300 --> 00:12:57.945
me darf ir rateven."

00:12:57.945 --> 00:13:02.870
un zi hot oykh genumen a nasn hantekh. zi hot zikh arumgebundn di GRUD',

00:13:02.968 --> 00:13:04.610
dem brust, ya?

00:13:03.197 --> 00:13:06.481
vu m'-... di brust... vu m'hot ir durkhgeshosn,

00:13:06.808 --> 00:13:13.957
un zi iz tsu tsu di shviger. zi hot ir oykhet arumgebundn mit a hantekh mit a nasn, ober zi iz oysgegangen.

00:13:14.267 --> 00:13:21.394
dan zogt di shvester mayne, zogt zi, "shver, git a kuk durkhn fentster: efsher zaynen nito shoyn di banditn.

00:13:21.394 --> 00:13:26.496
git a kuk." antkegn hot gelebt dokter Mats, a yidisher dokter.

00:13:28.122 --> 00:13:30.073
iz er aroys, der shver.

00:13:30.079 --> 00:13:35.350
er hot gezen, zey zaynen shoyn nito, di banditn. iz er aroys, un

00:13:35.350 --> 00:13:41.686
er hot gezogt az es lebt di shnur, geblibn geranet, me zol ir oyf gikh in BOL'NITSe avekfirn.

00:13:41.686 --> 00:13:44.920
hot er aroysgerufn SKOR⟨UNK⟩ PO- di gikhe hilf,

00:13:43.515 --> 00:13:44.820
gikhe hilf.

00:13:44.920 --> 00:13:50.680
er hot aroysgerufn di gikhe hilf, un men hot ir avekgefirt in di yidishe BOL'NITSe, oyf JAKŠTO.

00:13:49.295 --> 00:13:51.290
in di yidishe shpitol, ya?

00:13:50.680 --> 00:13:53.411
di yidishe shpitol oyf JAKŠTO gas.

00:13:54.868 --> 00:13:58.105
nu, iz dos hot di shvest- di meydl...

00:13:58.105 --> 00:13:59.920
ye, un di shtub,

00:14:00.403 --> 00:14:04.330
vu di mentshn zaynen geven oysgehargete, hobn zey farbrent,

00:14:04.330 --> 00:14:06.135
mit di mentshn tsuzamen.

00:14:06.462 --> 00:14:10.100
un azoy hot zikh mayn shvester, di eltere, geratevet.

00:14:09.904 --> 00:14:11.540
a farvundete, yo?

00:14:10.798 --> 00:14:12.378
a farvundete.

00:14:12.958 --> 00:14:19.815
iz di meydl vos m'hot gekhapt oyfn gas, un m'hot ir ar⟨a⟩- gebrakht oyfn zibetn fort, zi hot dos alts gevust,

00:14:19.815 --> 00:14:21.710
un zi hot dertseylt di mamen.

00:14:22.206 --> 00:14:29.304
zogt zi, "ir veyst az s'iz geven do a pogrom un ayer eyn tokhter iz geblibn, di Zelde iz geblibn lebn."

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:33.776
 di mame, farshteyt zikh, hot zeyer ongehoybn veynen.

00:14:34.727 --> 00:14:37.171
s'iz geven zeyer a groyser troyer,

00:14:37.171 --> 00:14:40.341
ober m'hot nit gevust oyf vos frier tsu troyern.

00:14:41.055 --> 00:14:43.330
nakher, in a tsvey vokhn arum,

00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:46.250
hot men undz aribergefirt oyfn nayntn fort.

00:14:46.995 --> 00:14:48.828
antshuldikt, un di tsvey vokhn,

00:14:48.852 --> 00:14:51.630
flegt men aykh gebn epes esn, trinken?

00:14:50.440 --> 00:14:54.347
 me flegt hirsh-kashe gebn, hirsh-kashe.

00:14:54.825 --> 00:14:56.658
⟨un⟩ vaser hot men gegebn.

00:14:56.682 --> 00:14:57.536
un broyt?

00:14:57.357 --> 00:15:04.821
neyn, mir hobn gehat dokh nokh fun veg. mir hobn zikh dokh gehat mitgenumen tsu lebelekh broyt, varenye; di mame hot gehat in, in,

00:15:04.821 --> 00:15:06.092
in kerbl.

00:15:07.313 --> 00:15:08.313
un...

00:15:07.380 --> 00:15:09.551
iz dos hobn mir gegesn.

00:15:08.697 --> 00:15:12.660
un der vos hot keyn zakh nit gehat? tsu zaynen geven tsvishn aykh azelkhene vos hobn ⟨k-⟩...?

00:15:12.072 --> 00:15:17.470
 nu, ikh veys nit dos fun di ershte, ken zayn az m'hot gegebn dortn a kashe esn. i-

00:15:17.691 --> 00:15:22.646
ikh ken nit altsenesding gedenken. dos iz ummeglekh tsu gedenken alts.

00:15:23.344 --> 00:15:28.839
nakher hot men undz aribergefirt oyfn nayntn fort. iz tsugeforn a GRUZOV- a GRUZOVIK.

00:15:27.830 --> 00:15:29.682
last-AV- last-mashin, ya?

00:15:29.301 --> 00:15:31.399
a groyse mashin

00:15:31.399 --> 00:15:32.656
iz tsugeforn,

00:15:32.656 --> 00:15:36.740
un mi- di mamen, mir, un nokh froyen

00:15:36.740 --> 00:15:38.810
hot men arayngezetst in mashin.

00:15:38.810 --> 00:15:40.720
az mir zaynen gezesn in mashin,

00:15:40.720 --> 00:15:44.128
hobn mir gezen vi oyfn barg zaynen geshtanen di,

00:15:45.028 --> 00:15:47.310
di merdeyrim, vi zol ikh zogn?

00:15:46.372 --> 00:15:47.750
di merder?

00:15:47.310 --> 00:15:50.298
di merder, un zey hobn geshosn oyf di mener.

00:15:50.298 --> 00:15:53.662
zogt di mame, "kinderlekh, mir hobn shoyn keyn tatn nit."

00:15:54.546 --> 00:15:57.950
un mer... mit dem hot zikh geendikt oyfn zibetn fort.

00:15:57.950 --> 00:16:00.250
undz hot men gebrakht oyfn nayntn fort.

00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:04.428
iz dortn gedenk ikh az k- a hirsh-kashe flegt men undz ale tog gebn esn.

00:16:05.228 --> 00:16:08.026
oyfn zibetn fort hot men undz oykh gehaltn

00:16:08.026 --> 00:16:09.373
tsen teg.

00:16:12.113 --> 00:16:16.818
nu, un nakher hot men undz fun zibetn fort gegebn di mamen a tsetl

00:16:16.818 --> 00:16:20.817
az men hot undz aroysgelozn, kedey keyner zol undz nit farhaltn

00:16:20.450 --> 00:16:22.760
UNK oyfn nayntn? oyfn na-...?

00:16:20.817 --> 00:16:23.666
oyfn gas. oyfn nayntn fort.

00:16:24.448 --> 00:16:26.703
mir zaynen gekumen in shtub.

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:34.638
⟨di sh-⟩ di shvester iz shoyn fun BOL'NITSe aroysgegangen; m'hot ir aroysgelozn,

00:16:34.638 --> 00:16:40.693
vayl m'hot nakher alemen geheysn geyn fun BOL'NITSe. ale yidn hot men geheysn geyn fun di BOL'NITSe.

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:44.760
zaynen mir geven tsuzamen epes,

00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:47.477
ikh veys nit vifl mir zaynen nokh geven in shtub.

00:16:47.787 --> 00:16:50.903
ober nakher hot men undz arayngetribn in geto.

00:16:51.364 --> 00:16:55.461
men hot undz arayngetribn in geto, zay- bin ikh geven,

00:16:55.461 --> 00:16:57.922
un nokh fir shvester,

00:16:59.042 --> 00:17:00.639
un di mame.

00:17:01.624 --> 00:17:03.580
keyn dire hobn mir nit gehat,

00:17:03.580 --> 00:17:06.886
nor mir hobn gelebt in a groysn langn barak,

00:17:06.886 --> 00:17:09.712
vos dortn zaynen geven toyznt mentshn,

00:17:09.712 --> 00:17:11.658
toyznt yidishe.

00:17:09.889 --> 00:17:10.889
UNK

00:17:11.597 --> 00:17:13.903
oyf vos far a gas iz geven der barak in geto?

00:17:14.517 --> 00:17:16.280
 ikh veys nit.

00:17:16.795 --> 00:17:19.236
kh'ken nit, kh'veys nit. tsu dos iz...

00:17:19.561 --> 00:17:21.141
ikh veys nit genoy.

00:17:22.093 --> 00:17:25.853
nakher zaynen mir dortn geven. keyn esn iz nit geven.

00:17:25.853 --> 00:17:28.039
di mame hot ibergepreglt,

00:17:28.039 --> 00:17:30.800
 alte ⟨monel⟩,

00:17:30.800 --> 00:17:33.107
vos der reyekh iz geven groys.

00:17:33.332 --> 00:17:38.236
ibergepreglt mit a tsiblke, un dos hot zi, di mame gemakht dortn far undz esn.

00:17:38.547 --> 00:17:41.038
nor ikh mit mayn kleyne shvesterl,

00:17:41.095 --> 00:17:42.827
zaynen mir gegangen

00:17:43.356 --> 00:17:45.392
betn a shtikl broyt.

00:17:46.990 --> 00:17:56.869
 mir zaynen gegangen a shtikl broyt, ⟨iz⟩ ver es hot dortn beser gelebt in geto flegt undz gebn, un mir flegn brengen bay di mamen, kedey di mame zol oykh hobn vos optsuesn.

00:17:56.869 --> 00:17:59.230
andere flegn undz gebn a teler zup,

00:17:59.230 --> 00:18:00.899
flegn mir esn mit ir,

00:18:01.108 --> 00:18:02.637
mit di shvesterl.

00:18:02.965 --> 00:18:05.642
nu, nakher iz geven di groyse aktsye.

00:18:05.682 --> 00:18:09.523
gevorn di groyse aktsye, zaynen mir ale avek oyf di aktsye.

00:18:09.175 --> 00:18:11.610
dertseylt, bite, vos iz dos, di groyse aktsye?

00:18:11.030 --> 00:18:16.225
 s'iz geven a groyse aktsye: men hot tsunoyfgek- -numen alemen

00:18:16.225 --> 00:18:17.353
fun geto,

00:18:17.781 --> 00:18:21.237
un men hot gezogt, "ver es vet blaybn zikh bahaltn,

00:18:21.237 --> 00:18:23.680
vet men shisn oyf an ort.

00:18:24.008 --> 00:18:26.634
ale darfn kumen oyf dem plats."

00:18:27.872 --> 00:18:29.250
un,

00:18:29.813 --> 00:18:33.148
ts- di groyse aktsye, tsen toyznt yidn

00:18:33.272 --> 00:18:38.400
vet men opteyln un me vet araynlozn in a kleyn geto, hobn zey gezogt,

00:18:38.487 --> 00:18:42.970
di vos kenen nit arbetn un vos hobn groys-, groyse familyes.

00:18:43.060 --> 00:18:45.799
azoy vi mir zaynen geven a groyse familye,

00:18:45.799 --> 00:18:47.747
finf kinder mit di mamen,

00:18:47.747 --> 00:18:49.830
iz tsu tsu undz eyner a...

00:18:49.830 --> 00:18:54.073
mir zaynen geshtanen a gantsn tog. mentshn zaynen shoyn geven farfrorn.

00:18:54.298 --> 00:18:56.463
andere zaynen nit oysgehaltn,

00:18:56.463 --> 00:19:00.290
hobn nit oysgehaltn; m'iz gef- m'iz gefaln direkt.

00:19:01.217 --> 00:19:06.099
geyt eyner tsu tsu undz, nit keyn bakanter. mit a muter

00:19:06.099 --> 00:19:07.336
iz er geven.

00:19:07.343 --> 00:19:10.560
un er zogt, "lozt zikh mir shteln far aykh.

00:19:10.600 --> 00:19:13.260
di mame mayne ken shoyn mer nit shteyn."

00:19:13.260 --> 00:19:17.709
hot mayn muter, mayn ma- mayn mame derzen az er hot a,

00:19:17.709 --> 00:19:20.350
a, a shayn.

00:19:21.062 --> 00:19:24.768
er hot gearbet bay dem glavnem daytsh fun geto.

00:19:23.430 --> 00:19:26.150
bay dem, bay dem hoypt-daytsh, ya?

00:19:25.095 --> 00:19:27.080
bay dem hoypt-daytsh.

00:19:27.492 --> 00:19:32.800
un er iz in gantsn mit eyn mamen, mer keyner nit. zogt zi, "nem⟨t⟩ bay mir a kind."

00:19:32.800 --> 00:19:37.326
vemen er hot nit gerufn fun di kinder, keyner iz nit gegangen.

00:19:37.326 --> 00:19:39.382
un mir hot er genumen far a hant,

00:19:39.726 --> 00:19:41.762
un mir zaynen durkhgegangen.

00:19:42.308 --> 00:19:45.154
az, az mir zaynen shoyn durkhgegangen

00:19:45.345 --> 00:19:50.621
hob ikh, ikh gib a drey di kop, az mayn mame mit di kinder zaynen shoyn nito, mit di shvesterlekh.

00:19:51.353 --> 00:19:54.317
ikh hob zikh fun im glaykh opgeteylt.

00:19:55.015 --> 00:19:57.911
mir zaynen durkhgegangen; ikh bin fun im glaykh avek.

00:19:57.951 --> 00:20:00.442
bin ikh geshtanen oyfn plats un kh'hob geveynt.

00:20:00.617 --> 00:20:02.943
"vu iz mayn mame? vu iz mayn mame?"

00:20:02.943 --> 00:20:05.533
iz tsu mayn shvester's a khaverte.

00:20:05.533 --> 00:20:09.082
hot zi mir derzen, zogt zi, "Merele, vos shteystu do?"

00:20:09.308 --> 00:20:12.240
efsher gedenkt ir dem nomen fun di shvester kh- khaver-...?

00:20:09.452 --> 00:20:10.452
⟨ge-⟩...

00:20:10.692 --> 00:20:12.780
⟨⟩, Simkhke.

00:20:12.648 --> 00:20:13.648
Simkh-...

00:20:12.780 --> 00:20:14.904
Simkhke hot men ir gerufn.

00:20:16.193 --> 00:20:18.752
nu, zogt zi, "gey in shtub.

00:20:19.197 --> 00:20:21.941
gey in shtub; di mame vet kumen."

00:20:22.082 --> 00:20:24.240
bin ikh avek in shtub.

00:20:24.833 --> 00:20:26.922
hob ikh moyre gehat arayntsugeyn;

00:20:26.922 --> 00:20:30.699
in koridor iz gezesn eyne aza nit, keyn normale

00:20:31.245 --> 00:20:35.913
mit a zak papir vos zi hot geklibn. iz zi, vayzt oys, oyfn plats nit gegangen,

00:20:36.207 --> 00:20:37.922
un m'hot ir nit geshosn.

00:20:38.974 --> 00:20:45.346
meyle, kh'hob, bin ikh geshtanen bayn tir, un ikh hob gevart, efsher vet nokh ver onkumen. fun toyznt mentshn

00:20:45.741 --> 00:20:49.610
bin ikh, eyne mit a kleyn kind oyfn hant iz gekumen,

00:20:49.610 --> 00:20:51.607
un epes nokh eyne a froy.

00:20:52.500 --> 00:20:58.005
 zaynen mir ale arayngegangen. s'iz shoyn geven fintster, bin ikh gelegn oyf di betl,

00:20:58.005 --> 00:20:59.251
kh'hob geveynt,

00:20:59.275 --> 00:21:01.125
un ikh bin azoy ayngeshlofn.

00:21:01.350 --> 00:21:03.895
in der fri, ikh her trit

00:21:03.895 --> 00:21:06.052
durkhn gr- langn koridor.

00:21:06.801 --> 00:21:10.204
hob ikh zikh oyfgekhapt un kh'hob a geshrey gegebn: "mame!

00:21:10.783 --> 00:21:12.470
mayn mame geyt!"

00:21:12.657 --> 00:21:16.886
ikh gib a kuk: es geyt arayn di Simkhke mit mayn shvester.

00:21:17.044 --> 00:21:18.730
 mit velkhe shvester?

00:21:18.073 --> 00:21:21.104
mit di eltste, vos iz geven geranet.

00:21:20.773 --> 00:21:22.440
farvundet, ya?

00:21:21.448 --> 00:21:26.639
m'hot ir opgeteylt fun di mamen un gezogt, "du bist yung; du kenst arbetn."

00:21:28.131 --> 00:21:30.369
dos iz geven di shvester Zelde, yo?

00:21:29.250 --> 00:21:34.233
Zelde, ye, vos iz geblibn fun fayer, vos zi iz aroysgegangen.

00:21:35.134 --> 00:21:38.975
nu, iz zi tsu, zogt zi, "Merele, mer hobn mir keyn mamen nit.

00:21:39.117 --> 00:21:40.984
mir hobn mer keynem nit."

00:21:41.901 --> 00:21:47.677
zog ikh, "to vu iz di mame?" zogt zi, "kh'hob gezen vi m'hot gefirt. mir, ⟨ikh bin⟩ geblibn bay, spetsyel bay di,

00:21:47.677 --> 00:21:49.846
 Simkhken shlofn,

00:21:49.846 --> 00:21:53.809
kedey mir zoln ophitn vu me vet ton, vos me vet ton mit di yidn,

00:21:53.983 --> 00:21:55.226
mit alemen."

00:21:55.300 --> 00:21:58.940
hobn zey gezen vi m'hot zey alemen gefirt oyfn barg,

00:21:59.215 --> 00:22:00.820
oyfn nayntn fort.

00:22:00.936 --> 00:22:04.240
un dan hot ir shoyn gevust az der naynter fort iz a toyter ort?

00:22:03.990 --> 00:22:06.480
neyn, mir hobn nit gevust.

00:22:06.589 --> 00:22:08.420
mir hobn nit gevust.

00:22:08.420 --> 00:22:10.549
m'hot zikh dos gornit forgeshtelt.

00:22:10.605 --> 00:22:15.166
dortn iz geven epes, mir hobn gevust az s'iz do a naynter fort, far Smetonasn nokh,

00:22:15.166 --> 00:22:21.440
ober dortn flegt men UNK araynzetsn mentsh-... ikh veys nit vemen, efsher komunistn, kh'veys nit.

00:22:21.895 --> 00:22:23.998
un dan, nakher hot men shoyn

00:22:24.055 --> 00:22:26.085
zikh genumen tsu undzere yidn.

00:22:26.085 --> 00:22:31.180
dortn iz shoyn geven der toyt-ort, vu me flegt alemen oyshargenen.

00:22:31.817 --> 00:22:34.679
nu, gornisht, ikh bin geblibn mit mayn shvester.

00:22:34.922 --> 00:22:37.244
zi hot arbetn nit gekent,

00:22:37.437 --> 00:22:39.230
vayl zi iz dokh geven geranet.

00:22:38.808 --> 00:22:40.280
farvundet, ya?

00:22:39.580 --> 00:22:41.008
farvundet.

00:22:41.942 --> 00:22:44.889
fleg ikh geyn in a kinder-brigade.

00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:49.327
ikh fleg geyn, dortn oyf di gertener arbetn.

00:22:49.519 --> 00:22:51.521
ikh fleg aroysloyfn.

00:22:52.270 --> 00:22:54.772
ikh fleg aropnemen di late di gele,

00:22:54.772 --> 00:22:57.640
un ikh fleg loyfn bay di Litviner in,...

00:22:57.640 --> 00:23:00.971
un oysbaytn oyf a shtikl broyt oder...

00:23:01.483 --> 00:23:04.666
nu, ⟨z-⟩ vos zey flegn gebn undz: bulves...

00:23:04.572 --> 00:23:06.390
un ir hot gehat vos tsu baytn?

00:23:06.597 --> 00:23:13.712
ikh fleg nemen bay mentshn; ikh hob nit gehat vos tsu baytn. iz hantekher, iz a lakn flegt men oysbaytn,

00:23:13.937 --> 00:23:16.980
iz ver a kleydl fleg gebn tsu farkoyfn,

00:23:16.980 --> 00:23:20.625
un ikh fleg dos alts oysbaytn, un nakher flegn mir zikh teyln.

00:23:20.625 --> 00:23:24.680
ikh fleg zey gebn, un far mir fleg ikh hobn.

00:23:23.450 --> 00:23:26.990
 vi groys iz geven di kinder-brigade? dertseylt a bisl merer.

00:23:25.830 --> 00:23:29.320
 di kinder-brigade iz geven mistome fun,

00:23:29.320 --> 00:23:35.919
efsher a hundert kinder flegn geyn. mit undz flegt mitgeyn a dokter. ⟨Kishenishkes⟩,

00:23:35.959 --> 00:23:37.742
zayn familye geven,

00:23:37.765 --> 00:23:39.092
der dokter.

00:23:40.363 --> 00:23:44.981
nu, nakher iz geven a brigadir. di familye gedenk ikh shoyn nit.

00:23:47.299 --> 00:23:50.077
dortn hot gelebt eyne a kristin,

00:23:50.134 --> 00:23:53.620
vos ir man iz geven der glavner bay undz.

00:23:52.493 --> 00:23:54.030
der hoypt, ya?

00:23:53.620 --> 00:23:58.678
der, er flegt undz oyfpasn. er flegt undz vayzn di arbet vos mir darfn,

00:23:58.678 --> 00:24:03.762
 arum- di groz raysn, arumarbetn di merelekh, burikes.

00:24:04.140 --> 00:24:06.817
nu, iz zayn froy

00:24:07.296 --> 00:24:09.841
flegt mir araynnemen bay zikh in shtub,

00:24:09.841 --> 00:24:12.605
un zi flegt mir gebn andere mol bulves sheyln,

00:24:13.168 --> 00:24:16.402
vos helfn. zi hot oykh gehat dray meydlekh,

00:24:16.982 --> 00:24:18.494
di, di kristin,

00:24:19.058 --> 00:24:26.370
un zi flegt oyf mir hobn zeyer rakhmones. zi hot gevust az mayn shvester iz geranet un ikh bin geblibn on tate-mamen, a kind.

00:24:26.370 --> 00:24:29.868
flegt zi mir andere mol onleygn in, in, rukzak

00:24:30.297 --> 00:24:33.620
a sakh produktn:

00:24:33.620 --> 00:24:37.243
"na, trog avek dayn shvester. zol zi dos hobn

00:24:37.266 --> 00:24:38.475
tsu esn."

00:24:39.190 --> 00:24:42.407
di familye ire iz BARAUSKIENĖ.

00:24:43.122 --> 00:24:45.428
un zi lebt nokh haynt? tsu ire ki-...

00:24:44.303 --> 00:24:46.330
zi lebt nokh haynt.

00:24:46.581 --> 00:24:48.130
un nakher,

00:24:48.842 --> 00:24:50.624
beys men hot shoyn...

00:24:52.082 --> 00:24:53.628
dos iz geven...

00:24:54.890 --> 00:24:59.470
 ikh bin geblibn shlofn di nakht bay di kristin,

00:25:01.448 --> 00:25:06.950
un, oyf morgn iz gekumen tsu geyn di brigade arbetn.

00:25:08.957 --> 00:25:15.583
iz der dokter ⟨Kishenishkes⟩ iz arayn bay ir. er fleg bay ir ale tog UNK zayn.

00:25:16.213 --> 00:25:21.843
zogt er, "du veyst, Merele, haynt hot men tsugenumen dray hundert yunge meydlekh.

00:25:21.900 --> 00:25:24.138
men hot zey avekgefirt arbetn.

00:25:24.567 --> 00:25:26.940
men hot zey avekgefirt in Palemon."

00:25:28.262 --> 00:25:34.550
ikh hob dos derhert, hob ikh ongehoybn veynen, un ikh zog tsu di kristin az ikh vil zayn mit ir tsuzamen.

00:25:34.708 --> 00:25:39.933
z- ir iz shver tsu arbetn, un oyb zi vet arbetn, alts eyns, ikh vil zayn mit mayn shvester.

00:25:40.311 --> 00:25:45.452
bin ikh gekumen in geto mit di brigade. tsurik hob ikh zikh umgekert in geto.

00:25:47.584 --> 00:25:52.134
un ikh bin gekumen in shtub dortn. mir hobn gelebt nokh mit yidishe;

00:25:52.275 --> 00:25:56.640
zey hobn mir arayngenumen mit di shvester, bay undz, vayl dortn dem,

00:25:56.640 --> 00:26:02.020
dem blok vu mir zaynen geven, der, ⟨d- in⟩ di la- gr- shtub fun di toyznt mentshn, hot men tsugemakht.

00:26:02.480 --> 00:26:05.094
 hot undz tsugenumen eyne a froy.

00:26:06.180 --> 00:26:10.570
Slove hot men ir gerufn, a bakante. mir mit di shvester hot zi arayngenumen.

00:26:10.570 --> 00:26:13.290
iz az ikh bin gekumen tsurik fun di kristin,

00:26:13.290 --> 00:26:16.232
⟨iz⟩ hob ikh shoyn take mayn shvester nit gefunen.

00:26:17.335 --> 00:26:18.493
bin ikh avek

00:26:18.550 --> 00:26:21.410
bayn glavnem in geto.

00:26:20.501 --> 00:26:22.630
bayn hoypt. a yid, tsu a...?

00:26:21.410 --> 00:26:24.360
bayn... a yid, Liptser.

00:26:24.962 --> 00:26:27.251
er iz geven der glavner in geto.

00:26:26.310 --> 00:26:28.140
der hoypt-mentsh, ya?

00:26:27.308 --> 00:26:28.213
ya.

00:26:28.540 --> 00:26:30.441
zog ikh,

00:26:31.003 --> 00:26:38.050
"ikh vil, bite, lozt mir forn in Palem- in Palemon tsu mayn shvester. firt mir avek bay mayn shvester!"

00:26:38.050 --> 00:26:41.250
zogt er, "du bist nokh a kind un dortn darf men arbetn shver."

00:26:41.250 --> 00:26:44.593
zog ikh, "ikh bin a kind, ober ikh ken arbetn ale arbet.

00:26:44.593 --> 00:26:46.455
ikh ken shver arbetn."

00:26:47.170 --> 00:26:52.901
zog ikh, "vayle dos iz mayn shvester eyn-eyntsike vos mir iz geblibn un ikh vil zayn nor mit ir tsuzamen."

00:26:53.852 --> 00:26:56.647
⟨nu,⟩ zogt er, "veyst, es darf kumen a fur

00:26:56.738 --> 00:26:58.267
mit a v- a vogn

00:26:58.358 --> 00:26:59.837
nemen zakhn

00:26:59.843 --> 00:27:03.313
far zey, vayl m'hot zey avekgefirt on zakhn alemen.

00:27:03.775 --> 00:27:10.434
iz ze," zogt er, "bahalt zikh in di zakhn, krikh arayn in di zakhn, un du vest kumen azoy tsu dayn shvester."

00:27:10.609 --> 00:27:12.425
un azoy hob ikh geton.

00:27:13.123 --> 00:27:15.192
ikh bin gekumen in Palemon.

00:27:15.520 --> 00:27:20.180
efsher gedenkt ir, vifl tsayt iz, zayt ir gea- geven in der kinder-brigade?

00:27:19.950 --> 00:27:25.959
 in di kinder-brigade? mistome a yor tsayt flegn mir dortn ge- hobn mir gearbet in geto.

00:27:26.235 --> 00:27:28.670
a yor tsayt hob- flegn mir arbetn.

00:27:28.670 --> 00:27:30.802
ikh fleg nokh geyn far a malekh

00:27:31.500 --> 00:27:35.590
in, in, oyfn erodrom arbetn kedey tsu krign a puter-BROD.

00:27:35.078 --> 00:27:37.120
vos iz dos, geyn far a malekh?

00:27:36.377 --> 00:27:38.686
a malekh hot zikh ongerufn

00:27:38.686 --> 00:27:42.640
dos vos, di vo- d-, oybe zi iz geven a farmeglekhe,

00:27:42.640 --> 00:27:48.437
flegt zi arbetn nit geyn, un zi fleg koyfn a mentshn, er zol arbetn far ir.

00:27:49.152 --> 00:27:50.648
fleg ikh geyn.

00:27:50.569 --> 00:27:53.130
vos flegt ir krign far a tog arbet?

00:27:52.594 --> 00:27:57.903
a UNK gornit. zi flegt mir gebn produktn: zi flegt mir gebn gute puter-BRODn,

00:27:58.028 --> 00:28:02.699
zi flegt mir gebn bulves, kedey mir zoln hobn optsuesn, mit mayn shvester.

00:28:02.699 --> 00:28:05.540
ot dos iz geven, di, di batsolt.

00:28:05.402 --> 00:28:08.433
un in di kinder-brigade flegt ir muzn geyn yeder tog?

00:28:08.406 --> 00:28:14.644
⟨, s'iz,⟩ ale tog flegn mir geyn arbetn zumer, un vinter nit. vinter hobn mir nit gearbet.

00:28:14.380 --> 00:28:16.500
to ven flegt ir geyn far a malekh, vinter?

00:28:15.831 --> 00:28:20.480
vinter. vinter fleg ikh zikh arumviklen di fis ⟨un on-⟩ mit a,

00:28:20.480 --> 00:28:24.160
mit a shtrik farbindn dem mantl, un geyn oyfn erodrom,

00:28:24.160 --> 00:28:27.353
un zikh nokh makhn stalne, di hor makhn lang,

00:28:27.353 --> 00:28:31.590
 zikh makhn azoy kedey ikh zol oyszen stalne.

00:28:31.272 --> 00:28:33.350
vos flegt ir ton oyfn erodrom?

00:28:31.832 --> 00:28:36.600
 oyfn erodrom flegt men, ikh veys nit, oykh,

00:28:36.600 --> 00:28:42.639
me flegt dortn, dem plats flegt men darfn oysglaykhn.

00:28:42.848 --> 00:28:47.837
s'iz geven arbet. mir flegn firn in vagonetkes zhvir oystsushitn.

00:28:47.944 --> 00:28:49.389
s'iz geven arbet.

00:28:49.986 --> 00:28:51.830
zey ho- zey hobn gefunen.

00:28:49.993 --> 00:28:51.850
vifl sho hot gedoyer-...?

00:28:51.830 --> 00:28:54.720
mir flegn geyn arbetn,

00:28:54.720 --> 00:28:58.740
nu, kh'veys nit, fun in der fri biz fun ovnt flegn mir shoyn geyn.
